reviews.review:
Pros:
- Can be fun if you play with friends
- There are some funny situations

Cons:
- The new update which had the purpose to punish camp and tunnel made everything worse, playing survivor is no fun anymore, when 9 out of 10 match is facecamp & tunnel.
- Awfully lots of bugs
- Completely broken matchmaking
- The game has the most toxic community I've ever seen and behavior doesn't do shit about that;
- Constant hate massages if some other players don't like something, behavior still doesn't care;
- Every patch results more issue than it was before;
- Game is boring if you play enough, there is only one gamestyle;
- The cosmetics are more expensive than the game itself.
